				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "A key idea behind the [[Moldable Chat]] is to enable developers to contextualize the LLM interaction. In this context, an interesting case for code generation is creating specific tools for the LLM. A tool is essentially a function that receives arguments and returns a result (see [[Moldable Chat: Tool-augmented interaction]])."
			},
			{
				"__type" : "textSnippet",
				"children" : {
					"__type" : "snippets",
					"items" : [ ]
				},
				"createEmail" : {
