				"code" : "GtL gt \r\tgtPageExplanation: 'LLM tools by example';\r\tsendMarkdown: 'Build an LLM tool for adding two numbers. Create dedicated examples. Ensure they are green. Package the classes in a package called {{gtPackage:MyLlmPackage}}. Use {{gtClass:GtLMagritteToolForMethodsSource}} as blueprint.'"
